  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Nethermind devs implemented the txpool_content rpc call like it is documented in https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/wiki/Management-APIs#txpool. \r\n\r\nHowever, the documentation is wrong and geth does not return an inner array.\r\n\r\nSee: https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/issues/20502 and https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/issues/16144 \r\n\r\nI think nethermind should act like geth here and remove the inner array from the result.",
